Package: odsAPI
Type: Package
Title: An API wrapper package to download data directly from data portals created by Opendatasoft <https://www.opendatasoft.com/en/>
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Felix Lorenz
Maintainer: Felix Lorenz <ogd@tg.ch>
Description: Use the API of the data platforms created by Opendatasoft.
    Download Open Government Data (OGD), the data catalog, specific records or perform queries on datasets.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    httr,
    jsonlite,
    magrittr,
    utils
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
